data.description: Discover the allure of this 2022 townhome nestled in the serene Gilman Walk community, encompassed by a sprawling 100-acre conservation area that affords breathtaking vistas of mountains & rivers. Boasting an open-concept layout, seamlessly connecting the living room & dining area. The kitchen showcases premium upgrades, including quartz countertops, 42” cabinets, & a suite of stainless steel Whirlpool® appliances. Luxury plank flooring, two-tone paint, & recessed LED lighting represent just a handful of the interior design concepts that grace this home. Upstairs, you'll find the primary suite with a dual-sink vanity & walk-in closet, accompanied by two additional bedrooms & a second full bathroom. Minutes from I5 & Arlington amenities.
